..TEXT:
|e letizia era ferza del paleo~: "`And joy was the
whip of the top,' i.e., it was joy that made it (the light) spin.
Several times in the ^Paradiso~ Dante makes a swift rotary motion
the symbol of keen delight" (Gr).
