..TEXT:
|'l duca Gottifredi~: Godfrey of Bouillon, leader of
the first Crusade (1096), battled with the Saracens in the Holy
Land and became first Christian king of Jerusalem.  |vista~: The
object of ^trasse~ {v.46}.
..TCHR:
